在19世纪，[[新加坡|新加坡]]是[[大英帝国|大英帝国]]的[[殖民地|殖民地]]，与[[槟城|槟城]]、[[马六甲|马六甲]]共同组成了[[海峡殖民地|海峽殖民地]]。海峽殖民地的旗帜主体为[[英国国旗|英国国旗]]，在旗帜右方设计了三个金冠，每一个金冠代表一个殖民地<ref name='ngsfotw'>{{cite journal|title=The Flags of the British Empire|journal=[[国家地理_(杂志)|国家地理杂志]]|year=1918|first=|last=|publisher=National Geographic Society|volume=32|pages=383|url=http://books.google.com/?id=RQgVAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA383&dq=Straits+Settlements+Ensign|format=PDF|accessdate=2009-01-12|author1=National Geographic Society (U.S.)}}</ref>，作为海峡殖民地其中之一的新加坡在当时并没有自己的旗帜。[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间，[[大日本帝国|大日本帝国]]占领新加坡，开始了长达两年多的[[新加坡日治时期|新加坡日治时期]]。在日治时期，[[日本国旗|日本国旗]]成为了当时新加坡的旗帜，并用作陆军旗<ref name='foong'>{{cite book | last = Foong | first = Choon Hon | authorlink = | coauthors = Xie Song Shan | title = ETERNAL VIGILANCE: The Price of Freedom | publisher = Asiapac Books Pte Ltd | year = 2006 | location = Singapore | pages =115–16 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=6lQ_yzxFMuEC&lpg=PT121&dq=singapore%20flag&pg=PT121#v=onepage&q=singapore%20flag| isbn = 981-229-395-7}}</ref>。第二次世界大战结束后，新加坡重回英国治下，成为了大英帝国的[[直辖殖民地|直辖殖民地]]，并获得一面属于新加坡自己的旗帜。这面旗帜在设计上把原海峽殖民地旗帜的三个金冠变为一个<ref>{{cite web|title=Singapore, Flag of|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/1355507/Singapore-flag-of|publisher=[[大英百科全书|Encyclopædia Britannica]]|year=2008|accessdate=2008-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201110646/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/1355507/Singapore-flag-of|archive-date=2008-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Corfield | first = Justin J. | authorlink = | coauthors = Robin Corfield | title = Encyclopedia of Singapore | publisher = Rowman & Littlefield Publishers, Inc. | date = 2006-04 | location = | pages = 68 | url = | doi = | id = | isbn = 0-8108-5347-7 }}</ref>。

1959年6月3日，新加坡组成自治政府<ref name='wheatley'>{{cite book | last = Wheatley | first = Paul | coauthors = Kernial Singh Sandhu, Hussein Alatas, Institute of Southeast Asian Studies | title = Management of Success: The Moulding of Modern Singapore | publisher = Institute of Southeast Asian Studies | year = 1989 | location = | page = 1067 | isbn = 978-981-3035-42-3 }}</ref>。6个月后，新加坡国旗与[[新加坡国徽|新加坡国徽]]、[[前进吧，新加坡|新加坡国歌]]一同正式启用<ref name="toh"/>。1989年，时任[[新加坡總理|新加坡副总理]]的[[杜进才|杜进才]]在一次媒体采访中提到了新加坡国旗的制定和启用：
{{cquote|虽然我们当时只是大英帝国辖下的自治政府，但我们认为有必有将新加坡各个种族的人团结起来，建立新加坡共和国……除国歌外，我们也设计了国徽和国旗，而且我们始终认为新加坡国旗应当平等的飘扬在[[英国国旗|米字旗]]旁。<ref name="toh">{{cite interview|last=Toh|first=Chin Chye|authorlink=Toh Chin Chye|title=Dr. Toh Chin Chye [oral history interview, accession no. A1063, reel 1]|publisher=National Archives of Singapore|year=1989}}: {{cite web|title=State symbols|url=http://www.a2o.com.sg/a2o/public/html/etc/07_symbol.htm|publisher=Access to Archives Online (a2o), National Archives of Singapore|accessdate=2007-11-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6D2N5tkcM?url=http://a2o.nas.sg/|archive-date=2012-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}

新加坡国旗的设计工作共进行了两个多月，副总理[[杜进才|杜进才]]建议国旗的背景为全红，但[[新加坡内阁|新加坡内阁]]否决了这一建议，内阁认为背景全红的国旗影射[[共产主义|共产主义]]<ref name="zaubidah">{{cite web|author=Zaubidah Mohamed|title=The national flag of Singapore|url=http://infopedia.nl.sg/articles/SIP_488_2004-12-18.html|publisher=Singapore Infopedia, National Library Board|date=2004-12-18|accessdate=2007-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506210123/http://infopedia.nl.sg/articles/SIP_488_2004-12-18.html|archive-date=2008-05-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。据[[李光耀|李光耀]]称，在制定国旗时，[[华人|华人]]民众希望效仿[[中華人民共和國國旗|中華人民共和國國旗]]，在国旗上加五颗五角星；而[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]民众则希望在国旗上有一个[[月球|月亮]]图案。为了照顾不同种族的需要，五角星和月亮都被设计在了新加坡国旗上。<ref>{{cite book|author=李光耀|authorlink=李光耀|title=The Singapore Story: Memoirs of Lee Kuan Yew|location=Singapore|publisher=Times Editions|year=1998|pages=342–343|isbn=978-981-204-983-4}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.contactsingapore.sg/home/index.php/eng/content/download/2582/15510/version/1/file/Synergy_Sep,Oct09_Low-Res+(FINAL).pdf |title=National Pride |accessdate=2009-12-15 |date=September and October 2009 |format=PDF |work=Synergy |publisher=Contact Singapore}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>

1959年11月30日，《新加坡国徽、国旗、国歌法》获得通过，并开始实施，条例具体规定了国旗、国徽的使用规章，并对如何演奏国歌提出了要求<ref>Singapore State Arms and Flag and National Anthem Ordinance 1959 (No. 70 of 1959).</ref>。时任国会议员的[[信那谈比·拉惹勒南|信那谈比·拉惹勒南]]在向[[立法机构|立法机构]]解释新加坡国旗寓意时说：
{{cquote|国旗、国徽和国歌是新加坡人希望和理想的象征……她带给新加坡人自尊、自重。<ref>{{cite web|title=State symbols|url=http://www.a2o.com.sg/a2o/public/html/etc/07_symbol.htm|publisher=Access to Archives Online (a2o), National Archives of Singapore|accessdate=2007-11-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6D2N5tkcM?url=http://a2o.nas.sg/|archive-date=2012-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}
1962年9月，新加坡民众投票决定加入[[马来西亚|马来西亚联邦]]；1963年9月16日，新加坡正式加入马来西亚联邦，成为马来西亚的一部分，[[李光耀|李光耀]]亲自在新加坡升起了[[马来西亚国旗|马来西亚国旗]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ourstory.asia1.com.sg/merger/merger.html |title=Road to Independence – Merger With Malaysia |accessdate=2009-11-30 |year=1998 |publisher=Singapore Press Holdings |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013002423/http://ourstory.asia1.com.sg/merger/merger.html |archive-date=2013-10-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。1965年8月9日，新加坡退出马来西亚联邦后，星月旗又一次成为了新加坡国旗<ref name=flag>{{cite web|title=National Symbols and References: The National Flag|url=http://app.www.sg/who/42/National-Flag.aspx|work=Singapore Infomap|publisher=Ministry of Information, Communications and the Arts|year=2004|accessdate=2007-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427073323/http://app.www.sg/who/42/National-Flag.aspx|archive-date=2009-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 设计 ==
《新加坡国徽、国旗、国歌法》中说明了新加坡国旗的寓意：红底象征着世界友好、人人平等；白底象征着纯洁与美德；五颗五角星代表了国家的五大理想：民主、和平、进步、公正、平等。新月和五星的组合紧密而有序，象征着新加坡人民的团结和互助的精神<ref name="rules">{{cite web |url=http://app.www.sg/data/usermedia/documents/Singapore_Arms_And_Flag_And_National_Anthem_Rules.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5r7lKWdGk?url=http://app.www.sg/data/usermedia/documents/Singapore_Arms_And_Flag_And_National_Anthem_Rules.pdf |archivedate=2010-07-10 |title=《新加坡国徽、国旗、国歌法》 (Cap. 296, R 1, 2004 Rev. Ed. |accessdate=2009-11-19 |year=2004 |publisher=Government of Singapore |dead-url=yes }} as amended by {{cite web |url=http://app.www.sg/data/usermedia/documents/Singapore_Arms_and_Flag_and_Nation_Anthem(Amendment)Rules2007.pdf |title=Singapore Arms and Flag and National Anthem (Amendment) Rules 2007 (S 377/2007) |date=2007-07-16 |accessdate=2010-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100703004905/http://app.www.sg/data/usermedia/documents/Singapore_Arms_and_Flag_and_Nation_Anthem(Amendment)Rules2007.pdf |archivedate=2010-07-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Lee|first=Kuan Yew|authorlink=李光耀|title=The Singapore Story: Memoirs of Lee Kuan Yew|url=https://archive.org/details/singaporestoryme00leek|location=Singapore|publisher=Times Editions|year=1998|isbn=9812049835 (hbk.)|pages=[https://archive.org/details/singaporestoryme00leek/page/342 342]–343}}</ref>。在20世纪下半叶，由于[[星月|星月]]被公认为[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰主义]]的象征，新加坡的回教徒激进分子也视国旗为象征着回教<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ari.nus.edu.sg/docs/wps/wps09_120.pdf |title=Sustaining Islamic Activism in Secular Environments: The Muhammadiyah Movement in Singapore |accessdate=2009-12-15 |author=Syed Muhd Khairudin Aljunied |date=August 2009 |format=PDF |work=Asia Research Institute Working Paper Series No. 120 |publisher=National University of Singapore |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101226214029/http://www.ari.nus.edu.sg/docs/wps/wps09_120.pdf |archive-date=2010-12-26 |dead-url=no }}; Syed Muhd Khairudin Aljunied, 'The Role of Hadramis in Post-Second World War Singapore – A Reinterpretation', Immigrants & Minorities 25, 2, p. 167.</ref>。

新加坡国旗长宽比例为3比2；[[新加坡政府|新加坡政府]]则规定新加坡国旗红色底的[[彩通|彩通配色系统]]代码为032<ref name='mystory'>{{cite web |url=http://mystory.sg/content/1564 |title=National Symbols – The National Flag |accessdate=2009-12-17 |year=2009 |work=MyStory |publisher=National Heritage Board |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617191613/http://mystory.sg/content/1564 |archive-date=2010-06-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。据由新加坡新闻通讯及艺术部（MICA）发行的手册称，新加坡国旗可以放大或缩小，但颜色和图案必须正确<ref name=guidelines>{{cite web|title=National Symbols and References: The National Flag— Guidelines|url=http://app.www.sg/who/122/National-Flag-Usage-Guidelines.aspx|work=Singapore Infomap|publisher=Ministry of Information, Communication and the Arts|accessdate=2007-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090512232108/http://app.www.sg/who/122/National-Flag-Usage-Guidelines.aspx|archive-date=2009-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。MICA还提供三种国旗建议大小，分别是：915毫米×1370毫米、1220毫米×1830毫米和1830毫米×2740毫米<ref name=nskit>{{cite book | last = Ministry of Information, Communications and the Arts | first =  | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = The National Symbols Kit | publisher = Ministry of Information, Communications and the Arts | year = 2001 | location = Singapore | url = https://www.worldcat.org/title/national-symbols-kit/oclc/49823410 | doi =  | id =  | oclc = 49823410 | isbn = 8880968010 | access-date = 2019-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160602042707/http://www.worldcat.org/title/national-symbols-kit/oclc/49823410/ | archive-date = 2016-06-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|5}}。

== 规章和准则 ==
